episodes.title: Discussion "Former Cult Leader Shares Thoughts on Netflix's Dancing with the Devil"
episodes.description:
Timmy Gibsons calls himself an ex-cult leader. He was a pastor of a Pentecostal church, he culls Shekinah as a "cult" however it is a mild cult, and he breaks down the explanations Robert Shinn uses in the documentary. It also explains how scripture is used and twisted.  He admits not knowing any background and his information coming from the documentary.
